          time September 18th, 2008
          p Michail and Sarah watch Lion King, eat pizza, and hold hands.
        li.timeline__event.timeline__event--heart
          h3 Michail asks Sarah to prom
          time Spring 2010
          p Michail paints a heart-shaped puzzle to invite Sarah to prom.
        li.timeline__event.timeline__event--college
          h3 Michail &amp; Sarah part ways for college
          time August 2011
          p Michail attends RIT in Rochester, NY
          p Sarah attends OSU in Columbus, OH
        li.timeline__event.timeline__event--house
          h3 Michail &amp; Sarah move in together
          time December 2013
          p After graduating from RIT, Michail moved to Columbus, joining Sarah while she finished school herself.
        li.timeline__event.timeline__event--vacation
          h3 Michail &amp; Sarah take their first, adult vacation together
          time July 2014
          p Michail and Sarah drive up from Columbus, OH to Sandusky, OH to visit Cedar Point Theme Park and Put-In Bay Island.
        li.timeline__event.timeline__event--sf
          h3 Michail &amp; Sarah move to San Francisco, CA
          time June 2015
          p Practically the second Sarah finishes school, Michail is eager to leave Ohio. So they drive across the country! Literally, less than a week after Sarah’s graduation.
        li.timeline__event.timeline__event--ring
          h3 Michail proposes to Sarah
          time February 10, 2018
          p Michail paints a puzzle to propose to Sarah.
          p They make an AMAZING 5 course dinner, and Michail reveals his puzzle during the tea course (at 1:30 in the morning!).
        li.timeline__event.timeline__event--seattle
          h3 Michail &amp; Sarah move to Seattle, WA
          time May 2018
          p Ready for something new, Sarah and Michail head off to the next place.
        li.timeline__event.timeline__event--wedding
          h3 Michail &amp; Sarah get married!
          time September 08 2018
          p 10 days from their 10-year anniversary! Their anniversary swaps from 09-18-08 to 09-08-18.

    section#photos
